Veterans Memorial, Angelina County.  In grateful memory of those who gave their lives for our country in World War II, Korean War and Vietnam War, erected by the citizens of Angelina County, sponsored by Angelina Post. No. 113, the American Legion.
Vietnam War, December 22, 1961, May 7, 1975; 
Korean War, June 25, 1950, January 31, 1955; 
World War II, December 7, 1941, December 31, 1946
